original_title: The Wild World of Eugen Vöhrmann
overview: Included in this package of three hours of nudies from the 60's and early 70's are "Gorilla and the stripper", "Laila wakes up", "Laila takes a bath", "Completely naked", "The nudist colony", "Motel Eroticon", "Three girls posing", "Dreamgirl" and many others. A lot from the Leena Skoog collection
